ActCooperative Credit Associations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Insurance Business (Cooperative Credit Associations) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the INSURANCE BUSINESS (COOPERATIVE CREDIT ASSOCIATIONS) REGULATIONS, in order to extend existing policy to the web pages of deposit-taking financial institutions, in order to help ensure a greater consistency between the promotion of insurance products permitted on the web pages of deposit-taking financial institutions and the promotion that is permitted in their branches.
